sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Telegram as Telegram Bot
    participant TeleService as Telegram Service
    participant EventSys as Event System
    participant TradingSys as Trading System
    participant LLM as LLM Agent
    participant Broker as Broker API
    participant MsgMgr as Message Manager

    Note over User,MsgMgr: Manual Analysis Trigger Flow
    
    User->>Telegram: /analyze
    Telegram->>TeleService: handle_analyze()
    TeleService->>EventSys: publish("trigger_workflow")
    EventSys->>TradingSys: _handle_workflow_trigger(event)
    TradingSys->>LLM: run_workflow(context)
    
    Note over LLM: LLM Agent Analysis Loop
    
    LLM->>MsgMgr: "🔍 Checking portfolio..."
    MsgMgr->>Telegram: Notification
    Telegram->>User: Message
    
    LLM->>LLM: get_portfolio_status()
    LLM->>LLM: get_market_data()
    LLM->>LLM: get_latest_news()
    LLM->>LLM: get_historical_prices()
    
    Note over LLM: Decision: Buy QQQ
    
    LLM->>MsgMgr: "💭 Analysis: Buy QQQ"
    MsgMgr->>Telegram: Analysis result
    Telegram->>User: Message
    
    LLM->>Broker: adjust_position("QQQ", 20%)
    Broker-->>LLM: Order ID: xxx
    
    LLM->>MsgMgr: "✅ QQQ adjusted to 20%"
    MsgMgr->>Telegram: Success notification
    Telegram->>User: Message
    
    LLM->>EventSys: schedule_next_analysis(4h)
    EventSys->>EventSys: Add scheduled event
    
    Note over LLM,EventSys: Workflow Complete

